# Monorepo

- pnpm workspaces: `apps/*`, `packages/*`
- Run tasks via `make run-frontend`, `make run-backend`, or `pnpm` / `turbo` from repo root
- Shared packages: `@repo/ui`, `@repo/eslint-config`, `@repo/typescript-config`

# Code style

- Minimize scope — one feature per change
- Reuse `@repo/ui` components before creating new primitives
- INR pricing, Indian pincodes, MRP vs selling price for e-commerce data
- API responses: `{ data }` success, `{ error: { message, code } }` failure

# File placement

- Backend API: `apps/backend/src/routes/`, `controllers/`, `services/`
- Frontend pages: `apps/frontend/app/`
- Shared types (when needed): new `packages/types` workspace
